ek Gj\u00f8nnes, Dennis B. Gaustad og Mathilde Lundbaek har alle f\u00e5tt plass i en midlertidig kommunal barnehage. Stine Aspelund er f\u00f8rskolel\u00e6rer i Aastahaugen barnehage."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4967874ea12e8446a055bf673e3977f9ee3859669b276f1d6fd1c39600ae27ec"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-06-17T20:31:19.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "F\u00f8r var det et dagsenter for eldre her. N\u00e5 har barna flyttet inn i Persaunet sykehjem."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1176430.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/BarnehagerHOVED"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/3955dd01bda553f435dd5548489b900883677cb2.jpg?58dd09ac"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Barna inn i sykehjemmet -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "3955dd01bda553f435dd5548489b900883677cb2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barn", "sykehjem", "barnehage"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["dennis b. gaustad og mathilde lundbaek", "persaunet", "aastahagen", "enja e. k. gaustad og mille m. s. riseth", "aastahaugen"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["h\u00e5kon alrek gj\u00f8nnes", "bente p. hansen", "emma usterud", "lyder r. hogstad", "stine aspelund", "mathilde lundbaek"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1176430.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/BarnehagerH